{
  "stem": "4670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "The policeman came to us after, I think this was about three weeks, and said, I would suggest that you don't open that store again.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I have been to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "The Gestapo was established then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "The Gestapo was something like you would call the secret police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "He said, you are on the blacklist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Blacklist means that if you don't leave, you will be going to jail.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I can assure you that's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "It may not be happening tomorrow, but it's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "So stay away from the store or do anything, but be careful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "So at that point, we decided that we had to leave Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not in 1933.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 19-- These things were subtle in 1933.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was coming later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What did happen, I forgot to tell you, the boycott did not just involve us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It involved a great many things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For example, I remember, on that same day that we had our incident, there were things that we didn't see, but they were in the newspaper because they loved to publicize it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took people off the street that they knew they looked Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For example, they had some people who were going to the Yeshiva, and, you know, they had the curls and the black hats.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they look different and they picked them out immediately.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had them scrub the gutter with toothbrushes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, they took photographs and it was well-publicized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Very shortly after that, they had the book burning at the Romer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Romer in Frankfurt is a very important landmark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the city hall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was actually the residences of royalty in the early years in the city of Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
